blppy install instructions

Built and tested with python 2.6 and blpapi (CPP) 3.4.8.1, on cygwin

1) Install BLPAPI from http://www.openbloomberg.com/open-api/

Select Windows C/C++

Unzip to /usr/local

2) Modify include and library paths to point to your BLPAPI installation

Lines: include_dirs and library_dirs

3) Build the python extension

$ python setup.py build

4) Install

$ python setup.py install

